Name: web
Description: Basic web search and content retrieval tools.
Version: 1.0

Overview:
This toolset provides simple web search and content fetching. It uses a
public search endpoint (DuckDuckGo HTML) and can fetch readable text from
URLs. These tools are best-effort and depend on network availability.

Commands:
- search
  Search the web and return a list of results.
  Parameters:
  - query (string, required): Search query.
  - num_results (integer, optional): Number of results. Default 5.
  - provider (string, optional): Search provider: ddg or tavily. Default ddg.
  - auto_parameters (boolean, optional): Tavily auto-config parameters.
  - topic (string, optional): Tavily topic (general|news|finance).
  - search_depth (string, optional): Tavily depth (basic|advanced).
  - chunks_per_source (integer, optional): Tavily chunks per source (advanced).
  - time_range (string, optional): Tavily time range (day|week|month|year).
  - days (integer, optional): Tavily days back (news).
  - start_date (string, optional): Tavily start date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - end_date (string, optional): Tavily end date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - include_answer (string, optional): Tavily false|basic|advanced.
  - include_raw_content (string, optional): Tavily false|markdown|text.
  - include_images (boolean, optional): Tavily include images.
  - include_image_descriptions (boolean, optional): Tavily include image descriptions.
  - include_favicon (boolean, optional): Tavily include favicon.
  - include_domains (array, optional): Tavily include domains.
  - exclude_domains (array, optional): Tavily exclude domains.
  - country (string, optional): Tavily country boost.
  - exact_match (boolean, optional): Tavily exact match.
  Returns: List of {title, url, snippet}.

- search_website
  Search within a specific domain using a site: query.
  Parameters:
  - query (string, required): Search query.
  - site (string, required): Domain, e.g. example.com.
  - num_results (integer, optional): Number of results. Default 5.
  - provider (string, optional): Search provider: ddg or tavily. Default ddg.
  - auto_parameters (boolean, optional): Tavily auto-config parameters.
  - topic (string, optional): Tavily topic (general|news|finance).
  - search_depth (string, optional): Tavily depth (basic|advanced).
  - chunks_per_source (integer, optional): Tavily chunks per source (advanced).
  - time_range (string, optional): Tavily time range (day|week|month|year).
  - days (integer, optional): Tavily days back (news).
  - start_date (string, optional): Tavily start date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - end_date (string, optional): Tavily end date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - include_answer (string, optional): Tavily false|basic|advanced.
  - include_raw_content (string, optional): Tavily false|markdown|text.
  - include_images (boolean, optional): Tavily include images.
  - include_image_descriptions (boolean, optional): Tavily include image descriptions.
  - include_favicon (boolean, optional): Tavily include favicon.
  - include_domains (array, optional): Tavily include domains.
  - exclude_domains (array, optional): Tavily exclude domains.
  - country (string, optional): Tavily country boost.
  - exact_match (boolean, optional): Tavily exact match.

- get_content
  Fetch a URL and return readable text.
  Parameters:
  - url (string, required): URL to fetch.
  - max_chars (integer, optional): Max characters to return. Default 4000.
  - text_only (boolean, optional): Return only text (default true).
  - include_title (boolean, optional): Include page title.
  - include_links (boolean, optional): Include links list.
  - include_images (boolean, optional): Include image URLs.
  - selector (string, optional): CSS selector to extract.
  - user_agent (string, optional): Custom user-agent.

- get_url_by_query
  Search and return the first result URL.
  Parameters:
  - query (string, required): Search query.
  - provider (string, optional): Search provider: ddg or tavily. Default ddg.
  - auto_parameters (boolean, optional): Tavily auto-config parameters.
  - topic (string, optional): Tavily topic (general|news|finance).
  - search_depth (string, optional): Tavily depth (basic|advanced).
  - chunks_per_source (integer, optional): Tavily chunks per source (advanced).
  - time_range (string, optional): Tavily time range (day|week|month|year).
  - days (integer, optional): Tavily days back (news).
  - start_date (string, optional): Tavily start date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - end_date (string, optional): Tavily end date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - include_answer (string, optional): Tavily false|basic|advanced.
  - include_raw_content (string, optional): Tavily false|markdown|text.
  - include_images (boolean, optional): Tavily include images.
  - include_image_descriptions (boolean, optional): Tavily include image descriptions.
  - include_favicon (boolean, optional): Tavily include favicon.
  - include_domains (array, optional): Tavily include domains.
  - exclude_domains (array, optional): Tavily exclude domains.
  - country (string, optional): Tavily country boost.
  - exact_match (boolean, optional): Tavily exact match.

- get_content_by_query
  Search and return the content of the first result.
  Parameters:
  - query (string, required): Search query.
  - max_chars (integer, optional): Max characters to return. Default 4000.
  - provider (string, optional): Search provider: ddg or tavily. Default ddg.
  - auto_parameters (boolean, optional): Tavily auto-config parameters.
  - topic (string, optional): Tavily topic (general|news|finance).
  - search_depth (string, optional): Tavily depth (basic|advanced).
  - chunks_per_source (integer, optional): Tavily chunks per source (advanced).
  - time_range (string, optional): Tavily time range (day|week|month|year).
  - days (integer, optional): Tavily days back (news).
  - start_date (string, optional): Tavily start date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - end_date (string, optional): Tavily end date YYYY-MM-DD.
  - include_answer (string, optional): Tavily false|basic|advanced.
  - include_raw_content (string, optional): Tavily false|markdown|text.
  - include_images (boolean, optional): Tavily include images.
  - include_image_descriptions (boolean, optional): Tavily include image descriptions.
  - include_favicon (boolean, optional): Tavily include favicon.
  - include_domains (array, optional): Tavily include domains.
  - exclude_domains (array, optional): Tavily exclude domains.
  - country (string, optional): Tavily country boost.
  - exact_match (boolean, optional): Tavily exact match.
  - text_only (boolean, optional): Normal web: return only text.
  - include_title (boolean, optional): Normal web: include page title.
  - include_links (boolean, optional): Normal web: include links list.
  - include_images_web (boolean, optional): Normal web: include image URLs.
  - selector (string, optional): Normal web: CSS selector to extract.
  - user_agent (string, optional): Normal web: custom user-agent.

- get_links
  Fetch a URL and return links.
  Parameters:
  - url (string, required)
  - user_agent (string, optional)

- get_images
  Fetch a URL and return image URLs.
  Parameters:
  - url (string, required)
  - user_agent (string, optional)

- fetch_json
  Fetch JSON from a URL.
  Parameters:
  - url (string, required)
  - headers (object, optional)
  - timeout (integer, optional)

- download_file
  Download a URL to a local file.
  Parameters:
  - url (string, required)
  - out (string, required)
  - timeout (integer, optional)

Usage Examples:
- search query="latest Groq models" num_results=3
- search_website query="installation" site="python.org"
- get_url_by_query query="OpenAI API pricing"
- get_content url="https://example.com/blog"
- get_content_by_query query="what is python" max_chars=2000
- search query="best pizza nyc" provider="tavily"
- get_content_by_query query="latest AI news" provider="tavily"
- get_content url="https://example.com" include_title=true include_links=true include_images=true
- search query="today tech news" provider="tavily" topic="news" days=7 include_answer="basic"

Behavior Notes:
- Search results are best-effort and may vary.
- Content extraction strips scripts/styles and returns plain text.
- Large pages are truncated to max_chars.

Dependencies:
- requests (optional) for HTTP
- beautifulsoup4 (optional) for better parsing
- Tavily API key in app/toolsf/web/.env for provider="tavily"
